# TaskFlow Project Overview

TaskFlow is a production-grade Trello-clone with multi-tenant Workspaces, built as a full-stack monorepo.

## Tech Stack
- **Backend**: Go 1.22+, Chi router, pgx, golang-migrate, bcrypt, golang-jwt, slog
- **Frontend**: React 19, TypeScript 6, Vite 8, Tailwind CSS v4, shadcn/ui, React Router v7, TanStack Query v5, @dnd-kit, Zustand
- **Database**: PostgreSQL 16
- **Infra**: Docker Compose, multi-stage Dockerfiles, Nginx

## Architecture
- Backend: handler → service → repository → PostgreSQL (clean layers, constructor DI)
- Frontend: @pages/ (route components) → @features/ (feature logic) → @hooks/ (TanStack Query) → @core/api/ (Axios)
- Import aliases: `@pages`, `@features`, `@components`, `@hooks`, `@utils`, `@core`, `@styles`, `@assets`, and `@/types` (not `@types` — conflicts with npm)

## Navigation Flow
Login/Register → Workspace List → Workspace Dashboard (stats + projects + members) → Project Detail (Kanban) → Task Modal

## URL Structure
`/login`, `/register`, `/workspaces`, `/workspaces/:wid`, `/workspaces/:wid/projects/:pid`

## Entities
User, Workspace, WorkspaceMember (owner/admin/member roles), Project (scoped to workspace), Task (todo/in_progress/done)
